        'hthpCol.rd.compressor.implication': '<strong>Engineering takeaway:</strong> The bottleneck is often the compressor and oil management, not the heat exchanger catalogue. Oil-free / maglev paths target long-run O&amp;M, frequent start-stop, and high-duty steam service.',
